{"tid":897384,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"連登左翼圍爐區（1）","createTime":"2018-11-10T23:29:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T23:29:25.000Z","uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d4f6faebc0b301da56489df56e05fb3df3bcbaff","tid":897384,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T23:29:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/897001/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/897001/page/1</a><br />\n開呢個po<br />\n主要係希望<br />\n各位ching分享下睇左翼理論相關書籍嘅心得／感想<br />\n無論係乜派別都好歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：唔係讀人文／社會學科，有錯屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: blue;\">書目推薦<br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a37zCEU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa37zCEU.jpg&h=7ead89d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講到左翼，肯定避唔開馬克思<br />\n但係你有無真係睇過佢嘅著作<br />\n睇之前／之後會唔會驚／覺得自己睇唔明，了解唔夠全面？<br />\n我自己覺得一本相當好嘅入門書<br />\n係Allen Wood寫、Routledge 2004年出版嘅Karl Marx<br />\n深入淺出<br />\n同你清一清乜嘢「歷史唯物主義」「異化」「剝削」之類嘅concept<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw<br />\n如果各位對康德有興趣<br />\n強烈推薦佢寫嘅Kantian Ethics<br />\n正到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}